%sql 

select gas_name, avg(price) 
from gas_stations
where gas_name is not null and 
    price is not null
group by gas_name

%sql
select date_time, avg(price) as avg_price
from gas_stations
where gas_name="${Gas Type=Gazole,Gazole|E85|SP95|SP98|E10|GPLc}" and 
                date_time like '${Year-Month [YYYY-MM]=2007-01}%' and 
                price is not null and 
                date_time is not null
                
group by date_time
order by date_time asc

%sql
select gas_name, avg(price) as avg_price,pop 
from gas_stations
where gas_name is not null and 
    price is not null and
    pop is not null and
    pop="${Type of Population=A,A|R}"
group by pop,gas_name
